column1: Source: Wittgenstein Centre for Demography and Global Human Capital (2018). Wittgenstein Centre Data Explorer Version 2.0
Educational Attainment Distribution by Broad Age

De facto population by level of educational attainment in a country or region, classified by sex and by broad age groups. Available in all scenarios and at all geographical scales. Figures are expressed as a percentage.
